A page that simulates a lantern, following the rules below:

Features:
- When open the page, the lantern is turned off and battery is 100%.
- When turn on the lantern, the battery decreases 1% of charge each second.
- When battery reaches 0%, the lantern turns off.
- When change the battery, restore 100% of it charge.

Layout:
- It must have a "Turn On/Turn Off" and a "Change Battery" button.
- It must show the lantern status and it's battery charge
- It must have responsive layout
- It must be creative!
